{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=<!--to be added-->|update|Todd intends to obtain the Alchemy Commission's medical book, ''Compendium of Remedies''. It's not shameful for a scholar to seek knowledge, but unfortunately he has to send you to the Alchemy Commission to fetch it for him.}}
