{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=<!--to be added-->|update|After the chaos in the Alchemy Commission, all applications need to be re-evaluated. Although Yuluo refused you, you found out that the ''Compendium of Remedies'' is not on the bookshelf. Perhaps, you should take a chance and look around nearby?}}
