{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=<!--to be added-->|update|In the midst of the conflict, medical books were scattered all over the place. After several obstacles, you finally managed to gather the ''Compendium of Remedies'' that Todd wanted. Hurry and bring the book back to him.}}
